    "pm-mrtgc8ad-1229-3dg2fd": {
      "id": "pm-mrtgc8ad-1229-3dg2fd",
      "type": "heading",
      "props": {
        "level": 1
      },
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "Intro"
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "b-m2-species-2": {
      "id": "b-m2-species-2",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "The most powerful ability of our species is the ability to transfer of knowledge from one mind to another"
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrtgc8ad-1230-0p7q9q": {
      "id": "pm-mrtgc8ad-1230-0p7q9q",
      "type": "list-item",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "This allowing so the next mind is able to pick up where the previous left off."
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "b-m2-lineage-3": {
      "id": "b-m2-lineage-3",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "Every leap in that technology shortened the distance between minds. "
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrp8188r-2789-zxxhcd": {
      "id": "pm-mrp8188r-2789-zxxhcd",
      "type": "list-item",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "Spoken / Physical language"
        }
      ],
      "children": [
        "pm-mrtgc8ad-1231-z2a7aq"
      ]
    },
    "pm-mrtgc8ad-1231-z2a7aq": {
      "id": "pm-mrtgc8ad-1231-z2a7aq",
      "type": "list-item",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "Transmission of knowledge from person to person"
        }
      ],
      "children": [
        "pm-mrtgc8ad-1232-q571fb",
        "pm-mrtgc8ad-1233-pdbtmn"
      ]
    },
    "pm-mrtgc8ad-1232-q571fb": {
      "id": "pm-mrtgc8ad-1232-q571fb",
      "type": "list-item",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "1 to 1 knowledge transfer"
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrtgc8ad-1233-pdbtmn": {
      "id": "pm-mrtgc8ad-1233-pdbtmn",
      "type": "list-item",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "Don't eat this berry, it kill you"
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrtgc8ad-1234-b3xnnd": {
      "id": "pm-mrtgc8ad-1234-b3xnnd",
      "type": "list-item",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "Written language "
        }
      ],
      "children": [
        "pm-mrtgc8ad-1235-3f3zbx"
      ]
    },
    "pm-mrtgc8ad-1235-3f3zbx": {
      "id": "pm-mrtgc8ad-1235-3f3zbx",
      "type": "list-item",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "Mass transmission capability"
        }
      ],
      "children": [
        "pm-mrtgc8ad-1236-hccuoc",
        "pm-mrtgc8ad-1237-8n7r6p"
      ]
    },
    "pm-mrtgc8ad-1236-hccuoc": {
      "id": "pm-mrtgc8ad-1236-hccuoc",
      "type": "list-item",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "1 to many possiblility"
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrtgc8ad-1237-8n7r6p": {
      "id": "pm-mrtgc8ad-1237-8n7r6p",
      "type": "list-item",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "Knowledge can outlive the author"
        }
      ],
      "children": [
        "pm-mrtgc8ad-1238-8yfezw"
      ]
    },
    "pm-mrtgc8ad-1238-8yfezw": {
      "id": "pm-mrtgc8ad-1238-8yfezw",
      "type": "list-item",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "IE, don't need to tell everyone not to eat the berry"
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrp8188r-2790-7rofu8": {
      "id": "pm-mrp8188r-2790-7rofu8",
      "type": "list-item",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "Diagrams"
        }
      ],
      "children": [
        "pm-mrtgc8ad-1239-kqt255",
        "pm-mrtgc8ad-1240-ol7vjv",
        "pm-mrtgc8ad-1241-yx271a"
      ]
    },
    "pm-mrtgc8ad-1239-kqt255": {
      "id": "pm-mrtgc8ad-1239-kqt255",
      "type": "list-item",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "1 to many"
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrtgc8ad-1240-ol7vjv": {
      "id": "pm-mrtgc8ad-1240-ol7vjv",
      "type": "list-item",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "Conveys an idea"
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrtgc8ad-1241-yx271a": {
      "id": "pm-mrtgc8ad-1241-yx271a",
      "type": "list-item",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "Cross languages"
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrp8188r-2791-gux0hw": {
      "id": "pm-mrp8188r-2791-gux0hw",
      "type": "list-item",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "The Internet "
        }
      ],
      "children": [
        "pm-mrtgc8ad-1242-ck8vvh",
        "pm-mrtgc8ad-1243-9ydjmo"
      ]
    },
    "pm-mrtgc8ad-1242-ck8vvh": {
      "id": "pm-mrtgc8ad-1242-ck8vvh",
      "type": "list-item",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "Near free access to all the information around the world"
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrtgc8ad-1243-9ydjmo": {
      "id": "pm-mrtgc8ad-1243-9ydjmo",
      "type": "list-item",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "New forms of media allowed for various flavors of 1 to many and many to many distribution"
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrp8188r-2792-is59wa": {
      "id": "pm-mrp8188r-2792-is59wa",
      "type": "list-item",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "AI "
        }
      ],
      "children": [
        "pm-mrtgc8ad-1244-kqr3nq"
      ]
    },
    "pm-mrtgc8ad-1244-kqr3nq": {
      "id": "pm-mrtgc8ad-1244-kqr3nq",
      "type": "list-item",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "Gives us the ability to sift through the mountains of information"
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrp9f073-1-8ek1px": {
      "id": "pm-mrp9f073-1-8ek1px",
      "type": "heading",
      "props": {
        "level": 1
      },
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "The Issue"
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrtgc8ad-1245-bt4bij": {
      "id": "pm-mrtgc8ad-1245-bt4bij",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "In the age of AI, the ideas we need to represent are rapidly gaining in complexity"
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrtgc8ad-1246-l9iouk": {
      "id": "pm-mrtgc8ad-1246-l9iouk",
      "type": "list-item",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "Before a system could be service that needs to balance users and such"
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrtgc8ad-1247-s3v19p": {
      "id": "pm-mrtgc8ad-1247-s3v19p",
      "type": "list-item",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "Now everything is becoming and massively complex autonomous distributed system"
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrtgc8ad-1248-rzgequ": {
      "id": "pm-mrtgc8ad-1248-rzgequ",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "Simple mermaid diagrams and hacky flowcharts done in Excalibur no longer fit the bill required to do these massive projects."
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrtgc8ad-1249-j618qz": {
      "id": "pm-mrtgc8ad-1249-j618qz",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "Further, as AI integrates to greater and greater capacities in our workflows, it can introduce slop and drift that we need to be able to fight against. "
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrtgc8ad-1250-lh26kn": {
      "id": "pm-mrtgc8ad-1250-lh26kn",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "We need to be able to clearly represent ideas about what the system is designed to do so that the AI will follow our desired intent. "
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "b-m2-gap-heading-5": {
      "id": "b-m2-gap-heading-5",
      "type": "heading",
      "props": {
        "level": 1
      },
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "The Gap"
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "b-m2-gap-physical-6": {
      "id": "b-m2-gap-physical-6",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "In the physical disciplines, the knowledge is written down."
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrp8188r-2795-jykqxb": {
      "id": "pm-mrp8188r-2795-jykqxb",
      "type": "list-item",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "A car ships with a repair manual that can walk a stranger from symptom to torque spec. "
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrp8188r-2796-juucno": {
      "id": "pm-mrp8188r-2796-juucno",
      "type": "list-item",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "A building leaves drawings detailed enough to renovate it a century later. "
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrp8188r-2797-ciaoa3": {
      "id": "pm-mrp8188r-2797-ciaoa3",
      "type": "list-item",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "etc"
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrp8188r-2798-qdefup": {
      "id": "pm-mrp8188r-2798-qdefup",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "Software does not have this"
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrp8188r-2799-ktkbyb": {
      "id": "pm-mrp8188r-2799-ktkbyb",
      "type": "list-item",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "Most software is API reference"
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrp8188r-2800-x9zuhv": {
      "id": "pm-mrp8188r-2800-x9zuhv",
      "type": "list-item",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "You are lucky if there is a single diagram in the docs"
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "b-m2-gap-excuses-7": {
      "id": "b-m2-gap-excuses-7",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "There were two excuses"
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrp8188r-2801-jxg83x": {
      "id": "pm-mrp8188r-2801-jxg83x",
      "type": "list-item",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "The pace of change of code was near impossible to keep the docs up to date"
        }
      ],
      "children": [
        "pm-mrp8188r-2802-4e88l3",
        "pm-mrp8188r-2803-9ql3fh"
      ]
    },
    "pm-mrp8188r-2802-4e88l3": {
      "id": "pm-mrp8188r-2802-4e88l3",
      "type": "list-item",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "Many people working on project, the intent drifts"
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrp8188r-2803-9ql3fh": {
      "id": "pm-mrp8188r-2803-9ql3fh",
      "type": "list-item",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "Everyone needs to know how to use the docs tools "
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrp8188r-2804-m40s4f": {
      "id": "pm-mrp8188r-2804-m40s4f",
      "type": "list-item",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "The tools were never built for it"
        }
      ],
      "children": [
        "pm-mrp8188r-2805-i9m5xb"
      ]
    },
    "pm-mrp8188r-2805-i9m5xb": {
      "id": "pm-mrp8188r-2805-i9m5xb",
      "type": "list-item",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "Most diagramming and docs tools are half baked as it wasn't a huge priority given the above"
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrp8188r-2806-zetj7z": {
      "id": "pm-mrp8188r-2806-zetj7z",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "Agents ended both. "
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrp8188r-2807-irnh0o": {
      "id": "pm-mrp8188r-2807-irnh0o",
      "type": "list-item",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "Agents can easily upkeep the docs as you make changes"
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrp8188r-2808-v73le7": {
      "id": "pm-mrp8188r-2808-v73le7",
      "type": "list-item",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "Tooling can now be easily made as what was once a whole product, has turned into a side project"
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrp8188r-2809-87ygvx": {
      "id": "pm-mrp8188r-2809-87ygvx",
      "type": "heading",
      "props": {
        "level": 1
      },
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "Why we Need This"
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrp8188r-2810-inp143": {
      "id": "pm-mrp8188r-2810-inp143",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "2 major shifts have happened with the advent of AI"
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrp8188r-2811-8x7dtd": {
      "id": "pm-mrp8188r-2811-8x7dtd",
      "type": "list-item",
      "props": {
        "ordered": true
      },
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "One builder is now able to (and should be) working on multiple projects at a time"
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrp8188r-2812-xaktnw": {
      "id": "pm-mrp8188r-2812-xaktnw",
      "type": "list-item",
      "props": {
        "ordered": true
      },
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "The projects you work on have meaningfully scaled in complexity"
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrp8188r-2813-vzgukk": {
      "id": "pm-mrp8188r-2813-vzgukk",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "They can carry the upkeep — and they raised the stakes, because one builder now runs several projects at once, each with the complexity that used to take a team. "
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrtgc8ad-1251-0zwfp2": {
      "id": "pm-mrtgc8ad-1251-0zwfp2",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "Comprehensive documentation has become a non negotiatable."
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrtgc8ad-1253-tqwwdv": {
      "id": "pm-mrtgc8ad-1253-tqwwdv",
      "type": "heading",
      "props": {
        "level": 2
      },
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "Trust is the point"
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "b-m2-trust-chain-14": {
      "id": "b-m2-trust-chain-14",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "Agents will continue to write more and more code. "
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrp8188r-2829-reu0y5": {
      "id": "pm-mrp8188r-2829-reu0y5",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "That only scales on trust."
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrtif752-80-y8t8e4": {
      "id": "pm-mrtif752-80-y8t8e4",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "Trust does not come from reviewing diffs faster."
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrtif752-81-11zpi8": {
      "id": "pm-mrtif752-81-11zpi8",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "Trust comes from knowing that the outputted code will match the initial intent you gave to the system. "
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrtif752-82-zc6fla": {
      "id": "pm-mrtif752-82-zc6fla",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "The underpinning idea here is our current documentation pieces do not actually fully capture our design and intent, and thus agents fail to be effective"
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrtif752-83-y0y0y3": {
      "id": "pm-mrtif752-83-y0y0y3",
      "type": "list-item",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "It is not their fault though as they are provided inferior intent"
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrp8188r-2833-gvlrua": {
      "id": "pm-mrp8188r-2833-gvlrua",
      "type": "list-item",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "Written down, that turns autonomy from drift into expansion — the system builds on your design decisions instead of guessing past them."
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "b-m2-trust-slop-15": {
      "id": "b-m2-trust-slop-15",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "Slop is what intent transfer looks like when it fails. "
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrp8188r-2834-bpmkij": {
      "id": "pm-mrp8188r-2834-bpmkij",
      "type": "list-item",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "An agent that cannot find the why fills the gap with plausible guesses, and plausible guesses compound. "
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrp8188r-2835-mckutg": {
      "id": "pm-mrp8188r-2835-mckutg",
      "type": "list-item",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "The fix is not a stricter reviewer at the end of the pipeline; it is a sharper definition at the top. "
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrp8188r-2836-i017ic": {
      "id": "pm-mrp8188r-2836-i017ic",
      "type": "list-item",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "Defining the identity of the software"
        }
      ],
      "children": [
        "pm-mrp8188r-2836-i017ic-gloss"
      ]
    },
    "pm-mrp8188r-2836-i017ic-gloss": {
      "id": "pm-mrp8188r-2836-i017ic-gloss",
      "type": "list-item",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "Exactly, durably, in a form both kinds of readers consume well — is the work this system is built for."
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "b-m2-divider-21": {
      "id": "b-m2-divider-21",
      "type": "divider",
      "props": {},
      "children": []
    },
    "b-m2-conviction-heading-22": {
      "id": "b-m2-conviction-heading-22",
      "type": "heading",
      "props": {
        "level": 1
      },
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "The Conviction"
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "b-m2-conviction-durable-23": {
      "id": "b-m2-conviction-durable-23",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "The docs are the durable artifact. The code is the current projection. "
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrp825fl-2842-dmjbpr": {
      "id": "pm-mrp825fl-2842-dmjbpr",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "When they disagree, the right question is not which file is newer — it is where the intent is most clearly preserved."
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "b-m2-conviction-bet-24": {
      "id": "b-m2-conviction-bet-24",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "When a better model arrives next year, hand it Foundation and System Design and you should get a better implementation back, with nothing lost in the handoff. "
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrp825fl-2843-ctj9xb": {
      "id": "pm-mrp825fl-2843-ctj9xb",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "That is the bet: intent outlives any one projection."
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
